sentences: Johannes "Hannes" Bauer (22 July 1954 – 6 May 2016) was a German trombonist of improvised music and free jazz.
From 1979 onwards, he worked as a freelance musician in Berlin.
Bauer died on 6 May 2016 at the age of 61.
